Play more than 50 levels within 3 different worlds.
Telekinetic gameplay: Move elements in the environment to create a path and clear the way.
Physics puzzles: Using real-time physics and a wide array of objects with their different properties, you can tackle a puzzle in your own way.
Multiple challenges: Time-attack, Achievements, secret bonuses, fragment collection or a minimum number of pause goals in each level. Also, speedruns optimized!

Overview:
Ethan: Meteor Hunter mixes puzzles and platformers core action mechanics with an innovative mechanic: telekinesis. Ethan can pause time and move objects around in order to solve puzzles and get though 50 levels with dynamic use of physics giving multiple gameplay and solving possibilities.
